By the way, Minecraft Live is on October 3rd for anyone interested in voting for a new mob.

Moobloom, a flower cow that may be useful with bees and looks a bit decorative

Glow Squid, which is a glowing squid that lives in the darker parts of the ocean

Iceologer, an illiger who lives in the new mountains and would make mountains more dangerous

Make sure to vote on Twitter, and let Rushia know about it!
